      "text": "These grimoires are not meant to prop up wobbly table legs. They are key to your servants' advancement. Each grimoire — be it common iron or precious ruby — can directly elevate a sorcerer servant's power by one rank. Simply use it once."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Each grimoire has its own rank, which determines the limit of power it can bestow. An iron grimoire cannot cultivate a diamond-level sorcerer, and a diamond grimoire can never reach the truth of ruby level. If you wish to obtain a ruby-level servant, you must first have a ruby grimoire in hand."
